The paper discusses provenance, which is a topic that is relevant to several subfields of computer science. However, the focus on a general-purpose programming language and the use of a tracing semantics suggest that the paper is most likely to be classified under databases (cs.DB), security and cryptography (cs.CR), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), or logic in computer science (cs.LO).
